01:02:32.880 --> 01:02:37.310
So for the bond rating agencies,
they also started with a user pays.

01:02:37.310 --> 01:02:39.220 position:56%
And so, if you subscribe to Moody's,

01:02:39.220 --> 01:02:40.790
