That financial engineering
produces securities that are really,

01:05:06.360 --> 01:05:09.820
really complicated, and there's
tranches [phonetic], and there's,

01:05:09.820 --> 01:05:11.500
you know, modeling going on.

01:05:11.500 --> 01:05:14.650
And basically it's so
complicated that the only people

01:05:14.650 --> 01:05:15.950
that can really understand
what's going

01:05:15.950 --> 01:05:18.430
on there are the mathematicians
and businesses who were hired

01:05:18.430 --> 01:05:20.020
to create them in the first place.

01:05:20.020 --> 01:05:21.810
Which is to say they
had a problem of how

01:05:21.810 --> 01:05:24.140
to market a security
